{"tid":1662080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足被捕後 一定一定要頂撚住唔好比警犬威逼利誘到","createTime":"2019-10-18T14:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T16:07:26.000Z","uid":61886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bba777b04f826b7cec882175b872f5322c26a115","tid":1662080,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇返依兩日既法庭文字直播<br />\n見到有手足被警誡下認罪<br />\n<br />\n我個人認知係老閪都唔認<br />\n因為搜證係警方責任<br />\n<br />\n如果認左罪<br />\n就好大機會比政府鋤死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n手足們 請頂撚住<br />\n啲狗只會想鋤死我地<br />\n死都唔好亂講野<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n我唔知係咪因為斷正所以認罪<br />\n定係律師有咩建議<br />\n如果有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姚 [同時干犯兩宗案件]<br />\n<br />\n1. 案發時，大批市民表達不同意見，被告用右手打證人一下，令證人感到害怕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>警誡下承認有打證人</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 兩枝汽油彈<br />\nTKO群眾 set rb 堵路 popo到場示威者逃去<br />\n被告在負責清理路障的Popo附近企圖燃點汽油彈，休班警到場將其制伏<br />\n被捕時，被告管有雷射槍 汽油彈 索帶 面罩<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">警誡下承認自行製造汽油彈</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n<br />\n黃XX<br />\n林XX<br />\n企圖縱火<br />\n十月十四日 旺角警署縱火<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">二人於警誡下聲稱仇視政府而縱火。</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n<br />\n三位手足都還押緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1bd48d386f3f1c71b3f47f4ac64443a54d3226","tid":1662080,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"推 手足們一定要知"},{"pid":"b3fb9555ece1bdeb0fbc97eee29888f516c4c7cd","tid":1662080,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFU7C5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFU7C5U.jpg&h=8c010635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddb8fec23a30012ab78dae0cf0556